Introduction

Sung Ji Yeon, also known as Jane, is a South Korean singer. She was the Main Dancer and Lead Vocalist of the girl group MOMOLAND.

She earned seventh place in the reality survival show "Finding Momoland", earning her a spot in the group. She debuted as a member of MOMOLAND on November 10, 2016 with their first mini album Welcome to Momoland. On February 14,2023, MOMOLAND announced their offical disbandment.
